                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Very high chance of showers. Winds northeasterly 20 to 30 km/h tending northerly before dawn then tending northwesterly 15 to 20 km/h in the late evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 11 with daytime temperatures reaching around 16.</text>
