            <forecast-period index="4" start-time-local="2026-07-01T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-07-02T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-06-30T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-07-01T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Very high chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm in the morning. Winds northerly 25 to 40 km/h turning northwesterly 30 to 45 km/h during the day. Overnight temperatures falling to around 11 with daytime temperatures reaching around 15.</text>
